AUDIO: 'Context 7 is a popular MCP server giving AI agents documentation about developer tools. But a lot of people don\'t know that VEL have released something that\'s much better. Meet open-source, a tool that downloads a whole repo into your project instead of looking for'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
