AUDIO: 'documentation because sometimes it\'s better for your coding agent to understand implementation details. You choose a project, it gets downloaded and then when [music] your agent actually has to use it, it can search through the code using open source. It also adds itself to the git ignore file and adds'

[00:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'an agents MD, giving an agent some instructions on how to use it. But why would anyone use this instead of cloning the repo themselves? Open source allows you to select a specific version, fetch multiple packages, list the existing'

